lastCommitMessage: Update agora_market_dart_sdk reference and enhance logistics system integration
- Updated agora_market_dart_sdk dependency reference in pubspec.yaml and pubspec.lock to a new commit hash for consistency.
- Refactored address management in AddAddressPage to support a new logistics system, including migration from the legacy system.
- Improved user interface for selecting shipping companies and service types, enhancing the overall address setting experience.
- Added migration information display to inform users of changes from the old system, ensuring a smooth transition.
